               <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview7.html\">\n                        <p>蓄電ソフト開発</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview8.html\">\n                        <p>応用機器設計</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview10.html\">\n                        <p>営業</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"navi__list--item\" data-page=\"technology\"><a href=\"/recruit_graduates/technology/\">\n                  <div class=\"list-wrap\">\n                    <p>未来をひらく技術力</p><span class=\"c-arrow-only-ico is-tab\"></span>\n                  </div></a></li>\n              <li class=\"navi__list--item\" data-page=\"internship\"><a href=\"/recruit_graduates/internship/\">\n                  <div class=\"list-wrap\">\n                    <p>インターンシップ</p><span class=\"c-arrow-only-ico is-tab\"></span>\n                  </div></a></li>\n              <li class=\"navi__list--item last-item has-child\" data-page=\"requirement\">\n                <div class=\"list-wrap js-has-child\" data-label=\"requirement\">\n                  <p>募集要項</p><span class=\"arrow-ico\" data-label=\"requirement\"></span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"child-list__wrap is-open\" data-label=\"requirement\">\n                  <ul class=\"child-list\">\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/requirement/\">\n                        <p>募集要項TOP</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/requirement/process.html\">\n                        <p>採用プロセス</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"header__entry--wrap\"><a class=\"header__entry--btn -white\" href=\"https://job.axol.jp/bx/s/nichicon_27/mypage/login\" target=\"_blank\">\n              <p>My Page</p></a><a class=\"header__entry--btn\" href=\"https://job.axol.jp/bx/s/nichicon_27/entry/\" target=\"_blank\">\n              <p>Entry</p></a></div>\n          <div class=\"sp-menu__btn\" id=\"js-menu-btn\">\n            <p>Menu</p><span class=\"border-ico\"></span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n    <div class=\"jobs\">\n      <div class=\"jobs-mv\">\n        <div class=\"jobs-mv__container\">\n          <div class=\"jobs-mv__img\">\n            <div class=\"c-container\">\n              <div class=\"c-ttl__contents\">\n                <h2 class=\"c-ttl white-txt u-textOverlay\"><span class=\"u-textOverlay__inner\">Jobs</span></h2>\n                <p class=\"c-sub-ttl white-txt u-textOverlay\"><span class=\"u-textOverlay__inner\">ニチコンの仕事</span></p>\n                <p class=\"jobs-mv__txt\">さまざまな職種が協力し、ニチコンの新たな未来を目指しています。</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"c-anchor-links\">\n        <div class=\"c-anchor-link\"><a class=\"c-btn\" href=\"#necst\">\n            <div class=\"c-btn__txt\">NECST事業</div></a></div>\n        <div class=\"c-anchor-link\"><a class=\"c-btn\" href=\"#condenser\">\n            <div class=\"c-btn__txt\">コンデンサ<br class=\"is-sp\">事業</div></a></div>\n        <div class=\"c-anchor-link\"><a class=\"c-btn\" href=\"#sales\">\n            <div class=\"c-btn__txt\">営業・<br class=\"is-sp\">管理部門</div></a></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"jobs-contents js-fadeup-trigger\">\n        <div class=\"jobs-contents__container\">\n          <section class=\"jobs-content\" id=\"necst\">\n            <div class=\"c-container\">\n              <h2 class=\"c-lower-ttl\">NECST事業</h2>\n              <div class=\"jobs-content__wrap\">\n                <div class=\"jobs-content__inner\">\n                  <div class=\"jobs-content__row\">\n                    <div class=\"txt-box\">\n                      <div class=\"c-lower-content__ttl\">システム・回路の開発</div>\n                      <div class=\"sub-ttl\">新たな急速充電器を生み出すための<br class=\"is-sp\">研究開発</div>\n                      <p class=\"txt\">高効率・高信頼・小型化・コスト競争力のある急速充電器の開発に向けて、急速充電器のシステム設計・パワエレ回路・制御回路の研究開発に取り組みます。電気回路系の他、システム設計者として情報系の方も活躍しています。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/jobs/jobs-content-img01.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"jobs-content__interview\">\n                      <div class=\"jobs-content__interview--inner\">\n                        <div class=\"ttl\">この職種の活躍フィールド</div>\n                        <div class=\"interview-list\">\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">電気</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state double\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">情報</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state double\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right u-padding\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">材料・化学</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">機械</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"jobs-content__wrap\">\n                <div class=\"jobs-content__inner\">\n                  <div class=\"jobs-content__row is-reverse\">\n                    <div class=\"txt-box\">\n                      <div class=\"c-lower-content__ttl\">ソフトウエアの開発</div>\n                      <div class=\"sub-ttl\">組込みソフトウェアの開発や<br class=\"is-sp\">機器UIを開発</div>\n                      <p class=\"txt\">性能を意識したOSレス電源制御ソフト開発から、機器UI(液晶パネルやスマートフォンアプリなど)、更には遠隔監視・制御システムの開発を行います。制御設計から実装(コーディング)までソフト開発の全工程を行っています。情報系出身者が多いですが、工学系出身者も幅広く活躍しています。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/jobs/jobs-content-img02.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"jobs-content__interview\">\n                      <div class=\"jobs-content__interview--inner\">\n                        <div class=\"ttl\">この職種の活躍フィールド</div>\n                        <div class=\"interview-list\">\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">電気</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">情報</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state double\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right u-padding\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">材料・化学</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">機械</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"jobs-content__wrap\">\n                <div class=\"jobs-content__inner\">\n                  <div class=\"jobs-content__row\">\n                    <div class=\"txt-box\">\n                      <div class=\"c-lower-content__ttl\">機構系の開発</div>\n                      <div class=\"sub-ttl\">高品質で使いやすい屋外機器を設計</div>\n                      <p class=\"txt\">屋外機器特有の設計要件を満足することで、高品質かつ使いやすい機器の開発を行います。高品質(故障しない)は勿論のこと、UI,UX,UDといったお客様との接点となる部分にも注力して取り組みます。機械系、材料系の方が多く活躍しています。</p>\n                      <div class=\"comment\">\n                        <dl class=\"comment-list\">\n                          <dt class=\"comment-list__ttl\">UI：</dt>\n                          <dd class=\"comment-list__txt\">ユーザーインターフェイス</dd>\n                        </dl>\n                        <dl class=\"comment-list\">\n                          <dt class=\"comment-list__ttl\">UX：</dt>\n                          <dd class=\"comment-list__txt\">ユーザーエクスペリエンス</dd>\n                        </dl>\n                        <dl class=\"comment-list\">\n                          <dt class=\"comment-list__ttl\">UD：</dt>\n                          <dd class=\"comment-list__txt\">ユニバーサルデザイン</dd>\n                        </dl>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/jobs/jobs-content-img03.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"jobs-content__interview\">\n                      <div class=\"jobs-content__interview--inner\">\n                        <div class=\"ttl\">この職種の活躍フィールド</div>\n                        <div class=\"interview-list\">\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">電気</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">情報</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right u-padding\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">材料・化学</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state double\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">機械</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state double\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </section>\n          <section class=\"jobs-content\" id=\"condenser\">\n            <div class=\"c-container\">\n              <h2 class=\"c-lower-ttl\">コンデンサ事業</h2>\n              <div class=\"jobs-content__wrap\">\n                <div class=\"jobs-content__inner\">\n                  <div class=\"jobs-content__row\">\n                    <div class=\"txt-box\">\n                      <div class=\"c-lower-content__ttl\">材料開発</div>\n                      <div class=\"sub-ttl\">高性能なコンデンサを目指した<br class=\"is-sp\">材料の研究開発</div>\n                      <p class=\"txt\">高性能なコンデンサを作るために、有機、無機にかかわらずあらゆる材料の特性を理解してコンデンサ用材料の研究開発に取り組みます。材料製造装置を内製しており、電気、機械系技術者も活躍しています。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/jobs/jobs-content-img04.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"jobs-content__interview\">\n                      <div class=\"jobs-content__interview--inner\">\n                        <div class=\"ttl\">この職種の活躍フィールド</div>\n                        <div class=\"interview-list\">\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">電気</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right u-padding\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">材料・化学</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state double\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">機械</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"jobs-content__wrap\">\n                <div class=\"jobs-content__inner\">\n                  <div class=\"jobs-content__row is-reverse\">\n                    <div class=\"txt-box\">\n                      <div class=\"c-lower-content__ttl\">製品設計</div>\n                      <div class=\"sub-ttl\">最適なコンデンサやモジュール品の<br>設計・シミュレーション解析</div>\n                      <p class=\"txt\">コンデンサは自動車、ICT機器などに不可欠です。ニーズに最適な電気性能のコンデンサやモジュール品を設計します。設計にはシミュレーション技術を活用します。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/jobs/jobs-content-img05.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"jobs-content__interview\">\n                      <div class=\"jobs-content__interview--inner\">\n                        <div class=\"ttl\">この職種の活躍フィールド</div>\n                        <div class=\"interview-list\">\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">電気</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state double\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right u-padding\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">材料・化学</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">機械</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state double\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"jobs-content__wrap\">\n                <div class=\"jobs-content__inner\">\n                  <div class=\"jobs-content__row\">\n                    <div class=\"txt-box\">\n                      <div class=\"c-lower-content__ttl\">生産技術</div>\n                      <div class=\"sub-ttl\">新しいモノづくりを実現する<br class=\"is-sp\">設備の開発・導入</div>\n                      <p class=\"txt\">デバイスビジネスの肝は生産技術です。材料開発、製品設計と連携して新しいモノづくり技術を確立し、それを実現する各種設備を開発、導入に携わります。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/jobs/jobs-content-img06.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"jobs-content__interview\">\n                      <div class=\"jobs-content__interview--inner\">\n                        <div class=\"ttl\">この職種の活躍フィールド</div>\n                        <div class=\"interview-list\">\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item u-border-right\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">電気</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state double\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"interview-list__item\">\n                            <div class=\"ttl\">機械</div>\n                            <div class=\"state-box\">\n                              <div class=\"state double\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </section>\n          <section class=\"jobs-content\" id=\"sales\">\n            <div class=\"c-container\">\n              <h2 class=\"c-lower-ttl\">営業・管理部門</h2>\n              <div class=\"jobs-content__wrap\">\n                <div class=\"jobs-content__inner\">\n                  <div class=\"jobs-content__row\">\n                    <div class=\"txt-box\">\n                      <div class=\"c-lower-content__ttl\">営業（国内・海外）</div>\n                      <div class=\"sub-ttl\">価値ある製品をお客さまへ</div>\n                      <p class=\"txt\">コンデンサ事業、NECST事業の環境負荷を低減できる製品をお客さまに提案します。技術系の営業職も活躍しています。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/jobs/jobs-content-img07.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"jobs-content__wrap\">\n                <div class=\"jobs-content__inner\">\n                  <div class=\"jobs-content__row\">\n                    <div class=\"txt-box\">\n                      <div class=\"c-lower-content__ttl\">管理部門等</div>\n                      <div class=\"sub-ttl\">企業価値最大化へ</div>\n                      <p class=\"txt\">生産管理、購買、法務、システム開発、経理、総務、人事等の部門があり、各部門が連携し企業価値の最大化を目指します。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/jobs/jobs-content-img08.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </section>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"c-container\">\n        <div class=\"interview-list\">\n          <div class=\"c-interview-article\">\n            <div class=\"c-interview-article__container\">\n              <h2 class=\"c-interview-article__ttl\">インタビュー記